Uses of Package
org.activebpel.rt.bpel

Packages that use org.activebpel.rt.bpel
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel Root package for the Active Endpoints Runtime for Axis (rtaxis).  
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.handlers Handlers translate between messages and protocol formats such as JAX-RPC or SOAP Document.  
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.invokers Contains impls of the actual rpc or document style invokers used to call out to external web services.  
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.rdebug.server Contains all server module for the ActiveBPEL remote administration and debug Web Services. 
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.receivers   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel This package contains classes for creating a BPEL model and for implements a standalone BPEL engine for testing designs. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.config This package contains the base classes for configuring the BPEL engine.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.coord This package contains the base classes for implementing coordination. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def This package contains base classes and elements used to create BPEL model definitions. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.faults   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io This package contains the BPEL reader and writer interfaces and the factory classes to access them. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.readers This package contains the default impl of the IAeBpelReader interface.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.readers.def This package contains the IAeBpelDefReader interface for reading in BPEL xml and the default impls. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.registry This package contains the registry classes for accessing readers and writers for BPEL and extension elements.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.writers This package provides the impl classes for the IAeBpelWriter interface.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation This package contains classes which support BPEL validation.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity This package contains implementation classes for activity validation models. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity.scope This package contains validation model implementation classes for scope related validation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors Classes implementing the Visitor pattern used to perform various functions on the activity definitions.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl This package contains the base classes used in the implementation model for the BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity This package contains classes used in the implementation model for the BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.assign This package contains implementation objects used for executing the assign activity. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.assign.from This package contains implementation classes used when executing the 'from' portion of an assign activity's copy operation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.assign.to This package contains implementation classes used when executing the 'to' portion of an assign activity's copy operation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.support Includes supporting bpel objects which aren't properly activities.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.wsio   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.wsio.consume Provides interfaces and classes for consuming WSDL message data by BPEL activities and other supporting objects (e.g., invoke activity, receive activity, and onEvent element of a pick activity).  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.wsio.produce Provides interfaces and classes for producing WSDL message data from BPEL activities (e.g., invoke and reply).  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.addressing   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.attachment   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.endpoints Endpoint reference factory, serializer, and deserializer.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.function   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.function.attachment   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.list List and filter facilities for Alarm, Message and Process.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.lock Locking facility used to control access to variables when there are serializable scopes in the process.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.queue Contains classes that model inbound and outbound messages from the engine as well as alarms.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.reply   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.storage Classes related to saving and restoring the state of processes.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.visitors Classes that visit a tree of BPEL implementation objects and save or restore their state.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server Root package for the Active Endpoints BPEL Engine.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.addressing Handles partner addressing (finding the correct endpoint reference for a given business partner).  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.addressing.pdef Handles partner definitions and addressing across all BPEL processes.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.admin Classes that manage queued receives and a bean that holds deployed process information.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.admin.rdebug.server   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.catalog   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.coord   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.coord.subprocess   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy Process deployment.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.pdd This package contains objects that are created during processing of the process deployment descriptor.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.validate Root package for the Active Endpoints BPEL Deployment Validation code.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine The BPEL engine, support classes, and engine factory.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.invoke   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.process This package contains classes related to process management.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.receive   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery This package contains classes for recovering or regenerating the state of a process from alarms, messages, or faults that the process received. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery.journal This package contains classes for representing journal entries for alarms, messages, or faults for possible recovery in the event of engine failure. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery.recovered This package contains classes for representing alarm or queue manager items recovered during the course of process recovery. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery.test This package contains classes for testing the functionality of the recovery engine. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.reply   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage This package contains classes for storing the state of BPEL processes to an external storage facility. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.attachment

org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.transaction   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.logging In-memory and persistent logging facilities.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.security   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.wsio.invoke   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.xpath   
org.activebpel.work The work manager and friends, which provide a facility for scheduling asynchronous operations.  
org.activebpel.work.input A specialized work manager that schedules work for processing input messages.
